Thank you for using cPark. We are already more than 5000 in Brussels and Antwerp!

This new version includes many new features:
- Real-time notification if a parking officer is reported near your car
- You can now create a user account
- You can ask to receive an alert when your parking time is over
- You can give us feedbacks directly in the app
- Plenty of other improvements

To speed up its European expansion, cPark becomes Seety!!! With 180 000 active members, we are by far the biggest parking community.

This new version contains some performances and design improvement. We also corrected a bug for the display of parking conditions and improved the autocomplete for the addresses.

Happy parking

To speed up its European expansion, cPark becomes Seety!!! With 180 000 active members, we are by far the biggest parking community.

This new version contains some performances and design improvement. We also corrected a bug for the display of parking conditions and improved the autocomplete for the addresses.

Happy parking

Good news! We added all public parking in Seety for Paris and Brussels. Rather handy if there’s no parking on the street or if you park for a longer period. Parking for other cities will be available very soon.

We also created a new menu ‘My maps’ that allows you to add additional information on the map. Parking spots for disabled people or boundaries of resident areas are already available in Paris and Brussels. Other info and new cities will be released very soon.

Don’t hesitate to let us know what kind of additional information you would like to have in the app.
A big thanks to all of you for your loyalty. We are already more than 205 000 Seetyzens. It’s just amazing!

Happy parking
